Punn tacho bapuy nokrechea nimtan boddodeak gelo ani thoinch vinobachem madhyomik ani uchch xikxonn zalem.

1913 vorsa to mettrikochi porikxa pas zalo.Inttoromiddiett porikxa divpakhatir 1916 vorsa mubom-i vochpak bhair sorlo.Punn vatteruch mubomycho marg soddun kaxik gelo.Thoim vinobhache odhyoin kelem.Lokmany ttillkachem tannem marg dorxon ghetlem,ani onvanni pamyamni 400moil cholun barikosannin sogllo moharaxttr polloilo.Gandhijichem bonaros hindu videapitthantolem dikxantobhaxonn aikolem.Tea bhaxnnacho vinobacher boroch probhavo poddlo.7 zun 1916 disa tannem gandhijichea ohmodabadchea kochrou axromant provex ghetlo.Modim ek vors to gandhijiche sangnnepromann,vaik svami keulononda mha-yant vedantachem odhyoin korpakhatir vochun raulo.Thoim upnixodam,gita brohmosutram,xankrobhaxy,monusmriti ani patonzol yogodrxon hea gronthancho tannem obheas kelo.Toxench nyaisutr, voixexik sutr, yagonevlkyosmriti he gronth vachle.Tannem gitecho vorg choloilo. Toxench vidhearthi monddllachi sthapnnuk keli.

Februvari 1918 to vinoba vaisaun porot ohmadabadek gelo.1921 vorsa gandhijicho onuyayi xetth zomnolal bozaz hannem sabromotichea soteagroh axromacho fantto vordheak ukto kelo.Tea fantteacho sonchalok mhonnun gandhijin vinobak vordheak dhaddlo..Tannem mognovaddi,bozazovaddi,mohilaxrom',sevagram' ani pounarak aplem senkary suru kelem.Hatunt sat-atth voram sut kamrop, vinnop ani xetkam' oxim kamam to kortalo.1930 ani 32 chea sovinoi kaidebhongache cholloullint tannem dhulleak bondkhonn bhogli.He bondkhonnint vinoban gitecher prouchonam dili ani sane gurujin tam boroun kaddlim.Sade-sompe bhaxent gitai hea namvan tannem gitecho moratthit onnkar kelo.

1940vorsa mohatma gandhin svorajea khatir voiyktik soteagrohachem andolon kelem.Ten'na poilo soteagrohi mhonnun gandhijin vinobak venchun kaddlo.Hea soteagrohant taka tin mhoine bondkhonn bhogchi poddli.

1951 vorsa soxstr krantivadi komyunisttamni telongonnant zominodaranche hol'le kele.Sat march 1951 disa andhrantlea xivramopl'li hea gamvant vochpa khatir vinoban sevagromasaun podeatra suru keli.Hi podeatra mhollear bhudanachem itihasik andolonuch axil'lem.18 epril 1951 disa andhr prodexant,pochmopl'li gamvant bhudanache kolponecho zolm' zalo.Ten'na vinoban dexbhor sadde postis hozar moilanchi podeatra keli.Bhartachea somazache dorxon gheun tacheo vyotha ddannun ghetleo ani xanticho updex korun pon'nas lakh ekrachem bhudan melloilem.Ti soglli ddomin bhumihinank vanttli.Saddetera vorsa hi podeatra kortokoch 1964 vorsa to porot sevagramak ailo.1970vorsa pounar hanga vochun kxetrosneas ghetil'leachem vinoban ddahir kelem.

